result.execSummary:
The defendant Blake A Burbach-Bull was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Blake A Burbach-Bull is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Blake A Burbach-Bull was found guilty of Theft-Movable Property <=$2500, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 943.20(1)(a).
  • Blake A Burbach-Bull was found guilty of Resisting or Obstructing an Officer, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 946.41(1).
